summary: The Bot Trust System Tokenomics - $WHOIS is a bot that enables users to identify alpha users and groups effortlessly. It provides a global social-proof catalog of crypto entities analyzed by AI. $WHOIS leverages a social-trust voting system for users and groups. The tokenomics of $WHOIS include a total supply of 10,000,000 tokens, a tax of 5%, no maximum transaction per wallet limit, and 5% of the supply allocated for CEX/Marketing.
